

To test this code you can:


## Clone the repository
```git clone https://github.com/Adamatt/Adventofcode```

## Install serve
```pnpm i -g serve```

## Step into the right folder
```cd /adventofcode/2024/day2/```

## Run a local server
```serve .```


Then open your browser and go to [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)


You will see the total number of safe red-nosed reports, and the list with green/red colors indicating weither the report is safe or unsafe.


You can navigate to the RNReport class and set the "unsafeTolerance" value to 0 in order to get the result of the first part.